Dialog e: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he became the Student Council President.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.09,0:00:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll announce it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.18,0:00:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I, Aisaka Taiga, am elected as Student Council President...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make this school mine and bury your high school life, along with your bloody memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in a mog... mog... morgue!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.26,0:00:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Palmtop Tiger is going to become Student Council President?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding me, cut it out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.07,0:00:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am her campaign manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.54,0:00:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have any problems, I'll deal with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.14,0:00:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.19,0:00:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he's quitting the student council and won't participate in the election.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why the Palmtop Tiger is running for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.95,0:00:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If any of you try to get in my way, I won't show you any mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.66,0:00:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Palmtop Tiger becomes Student Council President, our school life will be ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.09,0:01:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone help! Isn't there a brave soul who'll help us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! If Kitamura runs for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.35,0:01:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly, why isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.45,0:01:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're begging you, help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.09,0:01:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, our high school life will really be ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what the heck are you guys do{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.62,0:01:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A plan to get Kitamura back?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:23.10,Ep Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,400)\pos(907.272727,538.5)}One Step Forward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Since everyone will be troubled by Taiga,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.57,0:01:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no choice other than for him to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.00,0:01:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you think that if Kitamura-kun gets elected, he'll revert back to his old self?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not the only ones who think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.63,0:01:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I talked to everyone in the class on the phone last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.98,0:01:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they'll help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what that drama before was about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.90,0:01:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen if Kitamura-kun just refuses?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If no one else enters by this Friday,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.56,0:01:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka-san will truly become Student Council President.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.65,0:02:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun is definitely not the type of person to sit back and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.49,0:02:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to the office later. I'll teach you how to use the printer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.83,0:02:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to make posters and flyers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:23.68,Danger,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H5FC2E4&\bord0\shad2\fad(0,300)\pos(976,507)}Aisa{\c&H3333A2&}ka {\c&H5FC2E4&}Taiga
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.27,0:02:31.06,Chalk,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(558,99,478,99)\fs42\frz359}Taiga - Messenger from Hell
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:41.32,Danger,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz20\fs26\c&HEAEBEC&\shad1\pos(570,288)}Contract with a Demon\NAisaka Taiga's School Domination
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:09.14,Hand,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1066,342)\frz350\c&H423A34&}Speeches
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.10,0:03:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, Kitamura sure is a stubborn guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really thought it would work after all that effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one day left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we come up with another plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.02,0:03:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Is this Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never talked to you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.03,0:03:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Murase from the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.49,0:03:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're from the student council?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji, who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji, where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to beat the shit out of Kitamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wai{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.79,0:04:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanou, the current president, will be leaving next week to study abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably because of this, Kitamura is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.40,0:04:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I didn't tell you guys about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hold back too much, Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't tell anyone because I thought it was pretty lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I'm in love with the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Kanou-senpai is leaving for America next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she wants to be an astronaut.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A professor at an astronautics academy there personally accepted her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hadn't heard anything about this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:05:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I was planning to confess once I became Student Council President.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured she'd respect me by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.98,0:05:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, by the time I become Student Council President, she'll be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked myself if there were any other reasons to get elected,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and after thinking about it, I got scared and decided to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you dyed your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad finally exploded today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, he punished me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I {\i1}could{\i0} win her over, it's not like she'd give up her chance to study overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.24,0:05:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes don't always come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing really, I just thought of a similar conversation I had with Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone told her that things aren't progressing well for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, Taiga got mad and beat the person up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, as expected of Aisaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:05:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's on a completely different level.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I'd feel better if Aisaka beat me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.14,0:06:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you stupid dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.15,0:06:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know Aisaka became a candidate for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.26,0:06:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know everyone's worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I can't stay like this forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for listening to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.97,0:06:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.49,0:06:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made the decision myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you at school tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.15,0:06:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found you, Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:07:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you really...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.91,0:07:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what was that call about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, guys! Tomorrow is election day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll chase everyone who doesn't vote for me into the depths of hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, this school will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.77,0:07:28.23,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for before, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.64,0:07:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I will never allow something like this to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Kitamura Yuusaku, will definitely steer this school onto the correct path!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:07:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've made your decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure there hasn't been a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun still hasn't turned in his candidate form.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the rules, he can't run if it's not turned in by four.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.96,0:08:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Takasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka and the others are already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.37,0:08:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think they're going to that new café in front of the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four o'clock is the deadline for turning in your application.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, you'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home, Takasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no more time to think-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already thought about it. I think I'll give up after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.54,0:08:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't walked home together in quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:08:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the last time was when we were freshmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.04,0:09:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you're so busy with the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, I don't think I told you why I joined the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.47,0:09:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T... True.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really enthusiastic when I started at this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's what they call a high school debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first step towards a fun high school life is finding a girlfriend, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that there was this really beautiful girl in another class,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I decided to confess to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.99,0:09:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you already know this part.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was feeling really down after Aisaka rejected me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I met that person...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I saw everything, freshman.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't worry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your high school life has only just begun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Come join the student council!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said I'd feel better after doing some hard work there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.50,0:09:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that, I was brought to the student council room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:10:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since then, every day has been fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I even became good friends with Aisaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wish to have a fun high school life came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That uncertain first step I took after hearing her words led me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.23,0:10:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take the next step.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're going to run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the underclassmen who want you to become Student Council President?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to abandon them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.54,0:10:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're a man who would do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've lifted your foot already, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lifted it because you wanted to move forward, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what other choice do you have,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but to take a step forward?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:10:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't slack off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be watching what sort of Student Council President you become.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, what time is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3:58.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A superstar always appears at the last moment, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I have something important to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the candidates running for Student Council President will give their speeches.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the other candidate forfeited,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the only candidate is Kitamura Yuusaku-san from Class 2-C.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please welcome him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you heard, I am Kitamura Yuusaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,President, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.81,0:12:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm standing here today because I fell in love with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to confirm your feelings before you leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I really have no hope at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.13,0:12:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we not bonded by a special fate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.28,0:12:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a confession, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanou, answer him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You should give him an answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Kanou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:13:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you see, that is the Vice President Kitamura Yuusaku you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's interesting, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone as interesting as him becomes the president,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this school will definitely become interesting too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.57,0:13:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please give your precious vote to that interesting guy over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanou-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.37,0:13:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you answer him properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you tell Kitamura to move forward yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.34,0:13:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him to become a candidate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.63,0:13:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't tell him to confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you running away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Walking forward like an idiot is what they call "clumsy."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura needs to learn how to live his life wisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really a good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.36,0:14:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay good friends with Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wai{\fscx301.8868}-{\fscx100.62893} I'm not finished yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun is crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Ryuuji, stay by his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no help. I can't stay and comfort him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.59,0:14:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.67,0:14:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please go back to Kitamura-kun's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.06,0:14:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.71,0:15:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The thing you wish for the most is something you'll never get."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.12,0:15:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I came to understand that, I didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, Kitamura-kun smiled and held my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's such a kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot show him how grateful I am by a simple "thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.79,0:15:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand the one he likes isn't me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,however,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.21,0:15:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do what I can for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.93,0:15:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like he did for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.74,0:15:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanou...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sumire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It's the Palmtop Tiger?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I doing something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.31,0:15:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there's still an idiot left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:16:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in a good mood, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kendo club guys, lend me a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand who's wrong and who isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I know is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.79,0:16:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop moving forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.95,0:16:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! The Palmtop Tiger is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dumbasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.82,0:16:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the fuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.54,0:16:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a fucking coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.87,0:16:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just afraid you'll hurt others or you'll get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:16:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of your cowardice and foulness,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:17:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you hurt Kitamura-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my gosh, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.25,0:17:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just cowardly and foul!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.27,0:17:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a weakling who can't face her own feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.88,0:17:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if I'm a weakling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a violent bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nothing compared to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't accept Kitamura-kun's feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then say you hate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you understand about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.35,0:17:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could become an idiot like you, I would!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also want to be an idiot who only knows how to dash forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.34,0:17:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I say I like him, he'll follow me, won't he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he knew I wanted him to follow me, he'd do it, wouldn't he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.12,0:17:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the type of person who would sacrifice anything for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.71,0:17:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:18:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I can't be an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a really kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.51,0:18:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved you from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that I fell in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, before the teachers came here to control the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry for causing you so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.24,0:18:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.12,0:18:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a student ID while cleaning up just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like it belongs to Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then give it to Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.54,0:19:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, he's busy with the teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really does love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Underneath{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.06,0:19:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return this to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back to the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are your feelings of guilt gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:36.85,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanou-senpai spent her last day at school bruised.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:40.78,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Two days later, she left for America.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:45.90,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura received the honor of being Number One Pitiful Guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.90,0:19:47.24,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,and he became the Student Council President.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:52.14,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Taiga was suspended for two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:55.96,Hand,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H677372&\frz85\an9\fs24\pos(674,166)}Write an \Napology letter
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:24.71,Plain,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,800)\c&H746D68&\an8}Idiot
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:35.06,Preview Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\pos(323.636364,204)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:35.06,Preview Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs63\pos(650.909091,549)}Mercury Retrogrades at Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel Taiga will help you with your love life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll even take off her clothes for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it'd be troublesome if you catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your clothes back on.
